{"id": 825, "genre": 1001, "title": "你为什么不喝酒？", "description": "换句话说，你在什么情况下才会喝点儿？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3564, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183717Fk7Xmxwz3u9CWs4l.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-21T01:05:22Z", "options": [{"id": 51966, "content": "原则上的问题！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175545}, {"id": 52224, "content": "因为难喝 酒量也不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482199}, {"id": 52481, "content": "过敏严重我怕会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483027}, {"id": 52226, "content": "封（zhǔn）山（bèi）育（yào）林（wá）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237884}, {"id": 52227, "content": "來M!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408949}, {"id": 55043, "content": "真酒太贵，假酒易醉，说词不会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499445}, {"id": 82692, "content": "酒精难以接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624868}, {"id": 52228, "content": "喝的就不停", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55015}, {"id": 53508, "content": "不好喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479604}, {"id": 58116, "content": "不喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504131}, {"id": 51973, "content": "胃不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482753}, {"id": 52229, "content": "喝了以后自己算1+1=2，还好没断片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484099}, {"id": 51974, "content": "因为过敏…及其好的朋友和领导压迫下会喝一点，然后买药……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 11509}, {"id": 52230, "content": "开心或不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483732}, {"id": 51975, "content": "酒量不好 容易脸红 醉了难受", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482754}, {"id": 52231, "content": "终于痛风l", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108510}, {"id": 51978, "content": "不好喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219307}, {"id": 51979, "content": "跟好朋友一起的时候，想喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475010}, {"id": 51980, "content": "不知道喝酒的目的是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482779}, {"id": 51982, "content": "可乐更好喝！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 366738}, {"id": 51983, "content": "难喝，喝完头痛，睡不着，发冷，鸡皮疙瘩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482798}, {"id": 52239, "content": "在认为安全的情况下会喝。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115482}, {"id": 51984, "content": "我第一次喝啤酒是初中毕业，本来以为喝醉了能发泄什么，结果正好卡在没醉和头痛之间。。以后也不喝了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172256}, {"id": 52240, "content": "太苦了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305232}, {"id": 56848, "content": "因为打嗝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 51985, "content": "没有心情，没有故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477475}, {"id": 51986, "content": "酒不好喝，和好朋友才喝，完全看人", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482818}, {"id": 52242, "content": "领导让喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232378}, {"id": 58898, "content": "心情不好的时候就不是喝点儿了，喝到嗨好吗！", "image": "img/option/option/2016060614491589OCgZqAhGEULuyt.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 455019}, {"id": 52243, "content": "同家里长辈必喝，同好朋友可小酌，应酬偶尔。其余时候一概拒绝", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464142}, {"id": 53779, "content": "自己把自己喝吐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487372}, {"id": 51988, "content": "完全不胜酒力", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482830}, {"id": 52244, "content": "心情不好的时候，就会喝点。还有就是跟领导不得不喝的时候。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456860}, {"id": 51989, "content": "有酒胆没酒量，敢喝想喝易断片", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482831}, {"id": 54549, "content": "感觉有尿骚味！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496355}, {"id": 51990, "content": "人对，杯中有酒，自然嗨，人不对，酒太苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482832}, {"id": 52246, "content": "对面坐的人不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81342}, {"id": 51991, "content": "肠胃不好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482835}, {"id": 52247, "content": "喝酒是因为老爸退休了没有人陪他喝了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333084}, {"id": 52248, "content": "因为不好喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462474}, {"id": 60696, "content": "见过别人喝醉的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 51993, "content": "家庭聚会是会喝酒，不爱喝勾兑的酒；最不喜欢的就是饭都没吃冰啤酒下肚，不喝还说不给面，冰啤酒最容易反胃吐。但是白酒，黄酒，红酒这些你跟我来我奉陪到底", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238783}, {"id": 51994, "content": "花前月下可以喝，花钱日下就免了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482841}, {"id": 52250, "content": "因为着实讨厌老一辈人喝完酒后的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219236}, {"id": 51995, "content": "反感劝酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213130}, {"id": 52252, "content": "睡前喝一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215250}, {"id": 52508, "content": "事实上 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481632}, {"id": 51997, "content": "和聊得来的朋友…才会少喝一点吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482856}, {"id": 52253, "content": "酒太难喝了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416218}, {"id": 52509, "content": "我喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466315}]}